  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "In conclusion, after looking at all the points and stuff, it\u2019s honestly
    pretty clear that this whole topic is way more interesting than it maybe gets
    credit for at first glance. Like, when you really think about it, everything
    kind of connects in a way that makes you go \u201Chuh, that actually makes sense,\u201D
    even if it didn\u2019t at the start. Sure, there are probably more serious and
    professional ways to say all of this, but at the end of the day the main idea
    still stands and is, in my opinion, pretty solid. So yeah, taking everything
    into account, I would say this is why the argument works overall, and is why
    penguins are pretty rad."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8356cbc853111a843b01235b496037f2, type: 2}
